<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ka">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Configure Contest</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-light py-5">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 600px;">
        <div class="card shadow-sm border-0">
            <div class="card-header bg-dark text-white fw-bold">🔧 Contest Configuration: <%= contest.title %></div>
            <div class="card-body p-4">
                <form action="/admin/configure-contest/<%= contest.id %>" method="POST">
                    
                    <div class="mb-4">
                        <label class="form-label fw-bold small text-secondary">CONTEST DURATION (MINUTES)</label>
                        <input type="number" name="duration" class="form-control" value="<%= contest.duration %>" required min="1">
                        <div class="form-text small text-muted">შეგიძლიათ ნებისმიერ დროს გაზარდოთ ან შეამციროთ კონტესტის დრო.</div>
                    </div>

                    <hr>

                    <h6 class="fw-bold text-primary mt-3 mb-3">🔒 ALLOWED LIST (UPSOLVING CREDENTIALS)</h6>
                    
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label class="form-label small fw-bold">Allowed Username / Email</label>
                        <input type="text" name="allowedUser" class="form-control" value="<%= contest.allowedUser || 'checker' %>" required>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label class="form-label small fw-bold">Allowed Password</label>
                        <input type="text" name="allowedPassword" class="form-control" value="<%= contest.allowedPassword || 'checker' %>" required>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="alert alert-warning small border-0 p-2">
                        💡 კონტესტის ძირითადი დროის ამოწურვის შემდეგ, ამ იუზერით შესული ხალხი მაინც შეძლებს ამოცანების თავისუფლად გატარებას!
                    </div>

                    <div class="d-flex gap-2 mt-4">
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success fw-bold flex-grow-1">Save Configuration</button>
                        <a href="/contests" class="btn btn-secondary fw-bold px-4">Cancel</a>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>